<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Dogo Biscuits</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff7f32;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn,
        .verify-btn {
            background-color: #ff7f32;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .verify-btn {
            background-color: #3498db;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #ff7f32;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .divider {
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome, {{userName}}!</h1>
        <p>We're so happy you've joined the Dogo Biscuits community. To get started, we just need you to verify your
            email address. It's quick and easy!</p>

        <!-- Verify Email Button -->
        <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" class="verify-btn">Verify Your Email</a>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>After verifying your email, you can start exploring everything {{siteName}} has to offer. Simply click the
            button below:</p>
        <a href="{{siteUrl}}" class="btn">Visit Our Website</a>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions or need help, feel free to <a href="mailto:dogobuscuits@gmail.com">reach out to
                    us</a>!</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Dogo biscuits. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>